race.comment: KISSES FOR RUBY (2) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (19.54) at Hobart. Solid record at the distance winning seven races. Key chance in this line up. BUCKLE UP TAJA (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 515m behind Lizzy Milici (30.68) in a Grade 4. Was in the money prior to that. Cannot be left out. SIMPLY DANGER (3) copped a check in the run and boxed on to place when a 14 length third (30.44) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Worth another try. BUCKLE UP MILES (8) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.
